metadata.name: Sunny day at the foot of the volcano
metadata.description:
The plot of this artwork highlights the simple everyday life of an ancient society where dinosaurs are on a par with humans. They also work and have professions that often require a lot of physical effort, which is too much for a person. Dinosaurs are proud of their strength.
The artwork is done in the technique of engraving, etching.
When buying this NFT, I will send you the original of the engraving.
